xfsudo - run graphical applications as superuser using sudo
xfsu - run graphical applications as root using sudo -i

Requires-
zenity (https://wiki.gnome.org/Projects/Zenity)

Note- For this to work you need to put your user in the
sudoers file (see "man visudo").

## Installation

Install it as:

sudo make install

For Slackware users check out <a href="http://slackbuilds.org/repository/14.1/system/xfsudo/">xfsudo</a> at <a href="http://slackbuilds.org/">slackbuilds.org</a>

For Arch Linux users check out <a href="https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/xfsudo/">xfsudo</a> in the <a href="https://aur.archlinux.org/">Arch User Repository</a>

